# Dockerized OpenBikeSensor Scripts
Source: https://github.com/openbikesensor/OpenBikeSensor-Scripts

- 2 Docker Containers


## obs-wi-python
/obs-data/input
/obs-data/visualization (json output -> same as input below)



## obs-wi
Volumes:
/obs-uploads
/app/json   (json input)

## Development

### Collector
#### About
The "collector" accepts uploaded files from an OpenBikeSensor and stores them
on disk in the configured directory according to the environment variable
`OBS_UPLOAD_DIR`.

#### Running tests
Install dependencies
```shell
$> composer install
```

Execute tests
```shell
$> ./vendor/bin/phpunit tests
```
